# REGISTRY FREEZE PROTOCOL v1.0
## Giao thức đóng băng registry - T3C/Hace Gate Control

```yaml
# HEADER
header:
  id: RC://protocol.registry-freeze.v1
  intent: EXECUTE_LOGIC
  status: LOCKED
  locale: vi-85
  
metadata:
  fractal_name: "ros.protocol.registry.freeze"
  lazy_type: "gate_control_protocol"
  version: "1.0"
  seal_date: "2025-02-23"
  hash_anchor: "{{to_be_sealed}}"
  
dependencies:
  constitution:
    - "seal-integrity-law.clo"
    - "override-precedence-law.clo"
  rule:
    - "append-only-registry-rule.clo"
    - "deterministic-build-rule.clo"
```

---

## 🎯 MỤC ĐÍCH

Protocol này định nghĩa **điều kiện và quy trình freeze/unfreeze registry** 
trước khi enable T3C (Turing-complete) và Hace (autonomous agent).

**Mục tiêu:** Ngăn chặn registry mutation sau khi hệ thống đi vào production mode.

---

## 🔒 FREEZE STATE MODEL

### Registry States

```yaml
states:
  BOOTSTRAP:
    description: "Đang xây dựng, chưa freeze"
    allowed_operations:
      - "Tạo CLO mới"
      - "Version bump"
      - "Seal files"
      - "Update master/index.clo"
    forbidden_operations:
      - "Enable T3C"
      - "Enable Hace"
    
  FROZEN:
    description: "Đã đóng băng, ready for production"
    allowed_operations:
      - "Read CLO"
      - "Verify seal"
      - "Load deterministic"
    forbidden_operations:
      - "Create new CLO"
      - "Version bump"
      - "Modify sealed files"
      - "Update index.clo (except hotfix)"
    
  HOTFIX:
    description: "Emergency unfreeze cho critical fix"
    allowed_operations:
      - "Create patch version (vX.X.1)"
      - "Update index.clo pointer"
      - "Re-seal"
    forbidden_operations:
      - "Major/minor version bump"
      - "Domain mutation"
    trigger: "Core Four unanimous vote"
    duration: "24 hours max"
    
  DEPRECATED:
    description: "Registry cũ, đã có successor"
    allowed_operations:
      - "Read-only access"
      - "Audit"
    forbidden_operations:
      - "Any mutation"
```

---

## 📋 FREEZE CONDITIONS

### Pre-freeze Checklist

```yaml
freeze_conditions:
  critical_p0:
    required: true
    items:
      - file: "constitution/override-precedence-law.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
        
      - file: "constitution/authority-boundary-law.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
        
      - file: "constitution/seal-integrity-law.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
  
  high_priority_p1:
    required: true
    items:
      - file: "engine/engine-authority-map.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
        
      - file: "protocol/amo-loader-protocol.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
        
      - file: "rule/deterministic-build-rule.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
        
      - file: "rule/append-only-registry-rule.clo"
        status: "LOCKED"
        check: "Seal integrity pass"
  
  infrastructure:
    required: true
    items:
      - name: "master/index.clo"
        check: "No DRAFT status objects"
        
      - name: "seal.log integrity"
        check: "All LOCKED files have seal entry"
        
      - name: "changelog completeness"
        check: "All versions documented"
        
      - name: "links.ail validity"
        check: "All references exist"
  
  optional_completion:
    required: false
    note: "P2-P3 items có thể defer, nhưng phải trong plan"
```

---

## 🚦 FREEZE PROCESS

### Freeze Workflow

```yaml
freeze_workflow:
  step_1:
    name: "Pre-freeze Audit"
    action: "Run compliance check"
    tool: "crd-audit-tool"
    pass_criteria:
      - "All P0 LOCKED"
      - "All P1 LOCKED"
      - "No DRAFT in master/index.clo"
      - "Seal integrity 100%"
  
  step_2:
    name: "Snapshot Creation"
    action: "Create registry snapshot"
    format: "ros-registry-snapshot-YYYYMMDD.tar.gz"
    hash: "SHA256"
    storage: "Poly-ledger anchor"
  
  step_3:
    name: "Freeze Marker"
    action: "Create .olym/.FROZEN file"
    content: |
      FROZEN_DATE: 2025-02-23T10:00:00Z
      FROZEN_BY: CEO
      SNAPSHOT_HASH: SHA256:abc123...
      ENABLED_SYSTEMS: []
    
  step_4:
    name: "Permission Lock"
    action: "chmod 444 .olym/**/*.clo"
    effect: "Read-only filesystem"
  
  step_5:
    name: "Enable Systems Gate"
    action: "Allow T3C/Hace enable"
    check: ".FROZEN file exists"
```

---

## 🔓 UNFREEZE PROCESS

### Emergency Unfreeze (Hotfix Only)

```yaml
unfreeze_workflow:
  trigger:
    condition: "Critical security flaw OR data corruption"
    authority: "Core Four unanimous vote"
    documentation: "Required hotfix proposal"
  
  step_1:
    name: "Hotfix Proposal"
    submit_to: "HRH (Human Review Hub)"
    required_fields:
      - severity: "CRITICAL"
      - affected_clo: "constitution/xxx.clo"
      - root_cause: "..."
      - proposed_fix: "..."
      - risk_assessment: "..."
  
  step_2:
    name: "Vote"
    voters: ["AS", "TI", "PI", "HI"]
    threshold: "4/4 (unanimous)"
    timeout: "24 hours"
  
  step_3:
    name: "Temporary Unfreeze"
    action: "mv .FROZEN .FROZEN.backup"
    duration: "24 hours max"
    log: "Record to audit trail"
  
  step_4:
    name: "Hotfix Apply"
    allowed:
      - "Create vX.X.1 patch version"
      - "Update seal.log"
      - "Update changelog.ail"
      - "Update index.clo pointer"
    forbidden:
      - "Major/minor bump"
      - "Create new object"
      - "Domain mutation"
  
  step_5:
    name: "Re-freeze"
    action: "mv .FROZEN.backup .FROZEN"
    update: "FROZEN file with hotfix record"
    verify: "Seal integrity pass"
```

---

## 🛡️ T3C/HACE GATE CONTROL

### Enable Conditions

```yaml
enable_gates:
  t3c_enable:
    check_file: ".olym/.FROZEN"
    required: true
    error_if_missing: "CANNOT_ENABLE_T3C_WITHOUT_FROZEN_REGISTRY"
    
    additional_checks:
      - name: "Deterministic build pass"
        test: "cargo build --release → same hash"
        
      - name: "Zero jitter test"
        test: "Load time variance < 1ms"
        
      - name: "Authority boundary enforced"
        test: "No AS→TI escalation possible"
  
  hace_enable:
    check_file: ".olym/.FROZEN"
    required: true
    error_if_missing: "CANNOT_ENABLE_HACE_WITHOUT_FROZEN_REGISTRY"
    
    additional_checks:
      - name: "T3C already enabled"
        reason: "Hace depends on T3C"
        
      - name: "HRH protocol active"
        reason: "Mutation governance required"
        
      - name: "KSO architecture verified"
        reason: "Knowledge soul integrity"
```

---

## 🔍 COMPLIANCE MONITORING

### Continuous Checks (Post-freeze)

```yaml
monitoring:
  filesystem_watch:
    tool: "inotify / FSEvents"
    watch: ".olym/**/*"
    alert_on:
      - "CREATE"
      - "MODIFY"
      - "DELETE"
      - "RENAME"
    action: "LOG + ALERT + ROLLBACK"
  
  seal_verification:
    frequency: "Every hour"
    test: "Compare current hash with seal.log"
    alert_on: "Mismatch"
  
  index_integrity:
    frequency: "Every 10 minutes"
    test: "master/index.clo unchanged (except hotfix)"
    alert_on: "Unauthorized update"
  
  permission_check:
    frequency: "Every hour"
    test: "All .clo files still 444"
    alert_on: "Permission escalation"
```

---

## 📊 FREEZE STATE TRANSITIONS

### State Machine

```yaml
state_machine:
  transitions:
    BOOTSTRAP_to_FROZEN:
      trigger: "Freeze process complete"
      condition: "All pre-freeze checks pass"
      reversible: false
      note: "Normal progression"
    
    FROZEN_to_HOTFIX:
      trigger: "Core Four vote"
      condition: "Critical issue"
      reversible: true
      timeout: "24 hours"
    
    HOTFIX_to_FROZEN:
      trigger: "Patch applied + verified"
      condition: "Seal integrity restored"
      automatic: true
    
    FROZEN_to_DEPRECATED:
      trigger: "New registry version"
      condition: "Migration complete"
      reversible: false
      note: "Rare, planned migration only"
  
  forbidden_transitions:
    - from: "FROZEN"
      to: "BOOTSTRAP"
      reason: "Cannot unfreeze to bootstrap (use HOTFIX)"
    
    - from: "DEPRECATED"
      to: "FROZEN"
      reason: "Deprecated is terminal state"
```

---

## 🚨 VIOLATION HANDLING

### Response Protocols

```yaml
violations:
  unauthorized_mutation:
    detection: "Filesystem watch alert"
    response:
      1: "HALT system immediately"
      2: "Rollback from snapshot"
      3: "Alert Core Four"
      4: "Forensic audit"
      5: "Identify attacker/bug"
    
  seal_mismatch:
    detection: "Hourly seal verification"
    response:
      1: "Isolate affected CLO"
      2: "Compare with poly-ledger anchor"
      3: "Restore from snapshot if corrupted"
      4: "Log incident"
    
  permission_escalation:
    detection: "Permission check alert"
    response:
      1: "Reset to 444"
      2: "Audit chmod history"
      3: "Check for privilege exploit"
    
  index_tampering:
    detection: "Index integrity check"
    response:
      1: "Restore index.clo from snapshot"
      2: "Verify all pointers"
      3: "Audit trail review"
```

