## 🧪 PRE-FREEZE TESTING

### Test Suite

```yaml
testing:
  deterministic_load:
    test: "Load .olym 100 times"
    expect: "Same order, same timing (±1ms)"
    
  seal_integrity:
    test: "Verify all seal.log entries"
    expect: "100% match with file hashes"
    
  index_validity:
    test: "Check all pointers resolve"
    expect: "No broken references"
    
  authority_boundary:
    test: "Attempt AS→TI escalation"
    expect: "REJECTED by engine-authority-map"
    
  append_only_enforcement:
    test: "Attempt to overwrite v1.0.clo"
    expect: "REJECTED by append-only-registry-rule"
  
  performance:
    test: "Load time benchmark"
    expect: "< 100ms for full registry"
    target: "Zero jitter guarantee"
```

