## 🎯 SUCCESS CRITERIA

### Freeze Completion Checklist

```yaml
success_criteria:
  file_existence:
    - ".olym/.FROZEN exists"
    - "Snapshot in poly-ledger"
    - "All P0-P1 CLO sealed"
  
  permission:
    - "All .clo files → 444"
    - "Directories → 555"
    - "Root cannot write (enforced)"
  
  monitoring:
    - "Filesystem watch active"
    - "Seal verification running"
    - "Audit log enabled"
  
  gate_ready:
    - "T3C can query .FROZEN"
    - "Hace can query .FROZEN"
    - "Both systems aware of freeze"
  
  documentation:
    - "Freeze event logged"
    - "Snapshot documented"
    - "Team notified"
```

