## 🚀 POST-FREEZE OPERATIONS

### Allowed Operations in FROZEN State

```yaml
allowed_operations:
  read:
    - "cat v1.0.clo"
    - "view seal.log"
    - "grep links.ail"
  
  verify:
    - "sha256sum v1.0.clo"
    - "Check seal.log match"
  
  load:
    - "CLO loader read registry"
    - "Deterministic load"
    - "Cache building"
  
  audit:
    - "Forensic review"
    - "Compliance check"
    - "Performance profiling"
```

### Forbidden Operations in FROZEN State

```yaml
forbidden_operations:
  mutation:
    - "echo >> v1.0.clo"
    - "vi v1.0.clo"
    - "rm v1.0.clo"
    - "mv object-a object-b"
  
  creation:
    - "touch new-object.clo"
    - "mkdir new-domain"
  
  index_update:
    - "Update active_version (except hotfix)"
    - "Add new object entry"
```

